### CCR-013 §1, §3 — GE Upload + Download
###
### 검증:
### - POST /skins 201 Created (multipart upload)
### - GET /skins/{id} 200 OK (byte-exact 다운로드)
### - JSON Schema 검증 실패 시 422

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 20.1 POST /api/v1/skins — 정상 업로드
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="wsop-2026-test.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/wsop-2026-test.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

wsop-2026-test-override
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 예상 응답: 201 Created
# {
#   "id": "sk_01HVQK...",
#   "version": 1,
#   "etag": "W/\"1-abc...\"",
#   "url": "/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK..."
# }

### 20.2 GET /api/v1/skins — 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins?limit=20&offset=0&sort=-modified_at
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK + items[] + total

### 20.3 GET /api/v1/skins/{id} — .gfskin bytes 다운로드
GET {{host}}/api/v1/skins/sk_01HVQK-test
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/octet-stream

# 예상: 200 OK
# Content-Type: application/octet-stream
# Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="wsop-2026-test.gfskin"
# Body: ZIP binary (upload와 byte-exact 동일)

### 20.4 POST /api/v1/skins — JSON Schema 검증 실패
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="invalid-colors.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/invalid-colors.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# invalid-colors.gfskin 내부:
#   skin.json 의 colors.badge_check = "not-a-hex-color"
#
# 예상 응답: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# {
#   "error": "SCHEMA_VIOLATION",
#   "path": "colors.badge_check",
#   "message": "Pattern mismatch: expected ^#[0-9A-Fa-f]{6}$"
# }

### 20.5 POST /api/v1/skins — 파일 크기 초과
POST {{host}}/api/v1/skins
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="huge.gfskin"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./fixtures/huge-51mb.gfskin
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 예상: 413 Payload Too Large (50MB 제한)
